{
  "id": "adv_card_kkr_12_03",
  "title": "赤崎こころ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_rain-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "セットした髪が濡れてしまうぞ\n傘、持って来て良かったよ",
      "startTime": 3.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_03-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "わっ、びっくりした……{user}さん……\nすぐ戻るって言ったじゃないですか……",
      "startTime": 10.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "心配でつい、な……愛が来れないのは残念だが\n元気がないのはそれだけじゃないんだろう？",
      "startTime": 19.1348365136,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "大したことじゃないと言っていたが……\n学校で何かあったみたいだな",
      "startTime": 24.7666664124,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_03-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "さすがにごまかしきれないですよね……\nでも大したことじゃないんです、本当に",
      "startTime": 31.7333329519,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_03-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "最近……学校で席替えがあったんです\nそれで、隣の席の子と離れ離れになっちゃって",
      "startTime": 40.4000013988,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_03-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "さっきオフショ撮ってた時、偶然……\nその子が友達と一緒に歩いてたんです……",
      "startTime": 47.866669337,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_rain-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 49.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（あぁ、さっきの子達の中にいたってことか……）\n（思えばこころの学校から近い場所だしな）",
      "startTime": 55.6333377838,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_03-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "あの子は初めて、授業のノートを貸してくれた子で……\n私が話しかけてから、たまに話すようになって……",
      "startTime": 63.2666728973,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_03-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "でも、今は席が遠くなったので、ノートを借りる機会も\n話す機会もなくなりました……それだけの関係です",
      "startTime": 72.2666779835,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_rain-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 81.8000087737
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_03-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "ただ、ノートが借りれなくなって困ったなーって\n雨……酷くなってきましたし、戻りましょう",
      "startTime": 83.1549846939,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 88.8500031788
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 88.8500031788
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（仲良くなれそうな子が出来たのに、また一人に……か）\n（確かに、学校も楽しくなくなりそうだが……）",
      "startTime": 96.2128958459,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 99.7666698455
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "凄いな、こころは",
      "startTime": 99.7666698455,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_03-kkr008.m4a",
      "text": "な、なんですか急に……さっきの話から\nどうして私が凄いって話になるんですか",
      "startTime": 106.5666698455,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 110.4333365122
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "俺は学生時代、自分から一歩を\n踏み出すことなんて出来なかったからな",
      "startTime": 113.2638226375,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "今自分がこうしてこころのマネージャーをして\nいるのだって、ある人にきっかけをもらったからだ",
      "startTime": 118.3000031788,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 122.0333365122
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "だから頑張って、自分から一歩を踏み出した\nこころは、本当に凄いと思うんだ",
      "startTime": 124.8000031788,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_03-kkr009.m4a",
      "text": "私だって……自分から踏み出した訳じゃないです\nkanaさんに話を聞いてもらったから……",
      "startTime": 133.0000031788,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 135.8000031788
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "だとしても、隣の席の子に話しかけたのはこころだ\n行動を起こして、前へ進んだんだ、凄いことだよ",
      "startTime": 140.3333365122,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "友達は席が変わってもこころと話してくれるさ\nこのまま疎遠になったら……寂しいだろう？",
      "startTime": 149.6000031788,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 153.3666698455
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_03-kkr010.m4a",
      "text": "友達って……別にそんなんじゃないです\nノートを借りてただけですし、向こうも思ってませんよ",
      "startTime": 158.5333365122,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_03-kkr011.m4a",
      "text": "寂しいだなんて、ちっとも思ってないです\nむしろ清々してるぐらいなんですから",
      "startTime": 166.4214829336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 169.2333365122
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "おいおい、そんな言い方はダメだ\n友達が聞いたらショックを受けるぞ",
      "startTime": 172.6000031788,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_03-kkr012.m4a",
      "text": "だから友達じゃないんですってー、それに……\nノートを貸してくれた時から、距離感近くて",
      "startTime": 179.7666830698,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 184.1666830698
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_03-kkr013.m4a",
      "text": "まるで親友にでもなったみたいな態度で\nずっと話しかけてきてて困ってたんです",
      "startTime": 187.3333497364,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 190.6000164031
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_03-kkr014.m4a",
      "text": "それなのに席替えした後は……\n元々仲のいい子達とずっとお喋りしててうるさくて",
      "startTime": 193.2666830698,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_03-kkr015.m4a",
      "text": "さっきだって、その子達とぺちゃくちゃ話しながら\n歩いてたんですよ。楽しそうにずーっと笑ってて……",
      "startTime": 200.7333497364,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 205.6000164031
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_03-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "こころも、きっと楽しく話せるさ\n話を聞いてる限り、その子も悪い子じゃなさそうだし",
      "startTime": 208.7666830698,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 213.1333497364
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 218.3666830698
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_03-kkr016.m4a",
      "text": "だ、だから、こころは別に話したいとかじゃなくて……\nそもそも学校は勉強をするために通う場所です",
      "startTime": 218.3666830698,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_03-kkr017.m4a",
      "text": "友達とお喋りする場所じゃないのに……\n先生だって、そういうのも考慮して席替えするべきです",
      "startTime": 225.3333558399,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 229.6000225066
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_12_03-kkr018.m4a",
      "text": "そうです、先生のせいです！　職務放棄です！\n出るとこ出たらぜーったいにこころの勝ちですから！",
